{"tid":2403123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來裝安心出行係咁解","createTime":"2021-02-11T02:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T03:50:42.000Z","uid":121431,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35722da7e77ceb3cd5e37bec00920bfc168ece90","tid":2403123,"uid":121431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"話說想down個安心出行app同女朋友係情人節食返餐好既，點知比佢鬧。 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：bb 我地down 安心出行啦，我地情人節終於可以食餐好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女朋友：咩話，原來你係咁既賤人，睇錯左你，你情人節係屋企打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢仲係sd 左兩幅圖比我睇，叫我好好檢討下，到依家都仲未理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxK8SdB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxK8SdB.jpg&h=81cc0ace&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjYak60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjYak60.png&h=1e0388bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">政府我屌你老母，居然叫人偷食？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲陰9我搞到我比佢鬧，仲要情人節係屋企打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻唔撚裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">我係唔會偷食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好愛我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個裝即係偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"24fdf8dc04b5216730eee49736b004d4d6479f25","tid":2403123,"uid":121431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"推比更多人知，唔好中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49202a749191c03dd88f5d71d09b7e24eeaaa545","tid":2403123,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"尷"},{"pid":"3569ab4d367d25ffe6eba589917bcf0e98c7b114","tid":2403123,"uid":121431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b978bbbff937d90cc442ffcfb619594eb5aae6","tid":2403123,"uid":101541,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:27:06.000Z","msg":"唔好勉強"},{"pid":"3981183926be83c6384b847cc0c81d1d7f97901d","tid":2403123,"uid":121431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:27:14.000Z","msg":"情侶要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1e0e69bd2898915ce1e1e7856e9b6a8ac9518e","tid":2403123,"uid":232228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"😅"},{"pid":"5a757dbe5724213481324859673310fd20acaf0c","tid":2403123,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5db9bd20e9362105ca0258edc7bffd7c6ca6453","tid":2403123,"uid":355064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"用心良苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3ea6e1af9db35f66a09872703925a14c7f072